---
title: Venue - PyCon India 2025
description: PyCon India 2025 Venue at Nimhans Convention Center
layout: base.njk
isFront: true
---
{% from "components/button.njk" import button %}
{% from "components/card.njk" import card %}

<header>
    {% set activePage = 'venue' %} 
</header>

<div class="w-full h-[608px] bg-[#4E62F5]">
    <div class="pt-[200px] mx-[5%] md:mx-[145px]">
        <div class="black-han-sans-regular font-normal text-3xl md:text-5xl text-[#FFFFFF] text-center md:text-left">
            Nimhans Convention Center
        </div>

        <div class="absolute top-1/3 right-4 md:block">
            <img src="/img/assets/star-lime-vector.svg" alt="Groovy star" class="md:w-16 md:h-16 w-10 h-10">
        </div>

        <div class="absolute md:top-3/4 pt-52 md:right-20 right-24 md:block">
            <img src="/img/assets/star-purple-vector.svg" alt="Groovy star" class="md:w-16 md:h-16 w-10 h-10">
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:space-x-8">
            <div class="space-grotesk-regular font-medium text-xl md:text-2xl pt-8 text-[#FFFFFF] text-center md:text-left">
                <p>Nimhans Convention Center,</p>
                <p>Hosur Road, Lakkasandra,</p>
                <p>Bengaluru - 560029</p>
                <p>Landmark: Near Dairy Circle</p>
                <div class="pt-8">{{ button(text="Find Direction", url="#", lime_bg=true) }}</div>
            </div>
            <div class="justify-center md:pl-44 pt-12 md:pt-20 md:block hidden">
                {% call card(width=656, height=378, bg="lime") -%}
                    <img src="/img/nimhans-convention-center.jpeg" alt="Nimhans Convention Center" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
                {%- endcall %}
            </div>
            <div class="block md:hidden pt-12 mx-auto">
                {% call card(width=320, height=210, bg="lime") -%}
                    <img src="/img/nimhans-convention-center.jpeg" alt="Nimhans Convention Center" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
                {%- endcall %}
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="w-full bg-[#F0EEFF]">
    <div class="pt-[100px] mx-[5%] md:mx-[145px] md:pt-44">
        <div class="black-han-sans-regular pt-32 md:pt-32 font-normal text-3xl md:text-5xl text-[#000000] text-center md:text-left">
            <p>Getting to the</p>
            <p>Conference Venue</p>
        </div>

        <div class="pt-32 relative flex flex-col md:flex-row">
            <div class="flex-grow">
                <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                    <img src="/img/assets/train.svg" alt="Train" class="h-10 ml-0 md:h-28 mx-auto md:mx-0">
                </div>
                <div class="relative translate-y-[-132px] translate-x-2/4 w-[85%] mx-auto md:ml-16 md:w-[863px] md:block hidden">
                    {% call card(width=863, height=430, bg="lime") -%}
                        <div class="p-8 md:p-16 space-grotesk-regular">
                            <p class="font-bold text-xl md:text-2xl">Via Namma Metro</p>
                            <p class="pt-4 font-normal text-sm md:text-xl">From Green Line: Disembark at South End Circle or Lalbagh metro station. From the station, you can take a short taxi/auto ride to reach NIMHANS Convention Centre.</p>
                            <p class="pt-4 font-normal text-sm md:text-xl">For a list of stations on the Bengaluru Metro Green line, you can refer to <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Green_Line_(Namma_Metro)?oldformat=true" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline">Wikipedia</a>.</p>
                            <div class="pt-6 md:pt-10">{{ button(text="Green Line", url="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Green_Line_(Namma_Metro)?oldformat=true", lime_bg=true) }}</div>
                        </div>
                    {%- endcall %}
                </div>
                <div class="block md:hidden relative translate-y-[-72px] pl-16 mx-auto md:mx-0">
                    {% call card(width=280, height=380, bg="lime") -%}
                        <div class="p-8 md:p-16 space-grotesk-regular">
                            <p class="font-bold text-xl md:text-2xl">Via Namma Metro</p>
                            <p class="pt-4 font-normal text-sm md:text-xl">From Green Line: Disembark at South End Circle or Lalbagh metro station. From the station, you can take a short taxi/auto ride to reach NIMHANS Convention Centre.</p>
